{"tid":1704702,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"聽日三罷係對周同學屋企人一個交代","createTime":"2019-11-10T19:02:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-10T19:27:12.000Z","uid":163842,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"fad998cbea2eb2d360a7c9974069f1500d5b89b8","tid":1704702,"uid":163842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T19:02:42.000Z","msg":"手足已離開，剩低既事由我地做<br />\n聽日全港三罷係人性體現，全港用行動話比手足屋企人知我地都好傷心<br />\n<br />\n如果你聽日番工，我希望你行路，食飯時都諗下手足屋企人點面對<br />\n<br />\n唔好再比借口自己要被罷工，聽日係手足離開既第一個正式工作天，星期六日你驚，你無出黎唔緊要<br />\n<br />\n聽日見"},{"pid":"c0def11258aadc8f9b625782b66035e82ab5d664","tid":1704702,"uid":222970,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T19:03:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>我要番工 千祈唔好咁做!!!!!!!!!</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MG7Hx4n.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMG7Hx4n.png&h=41866d85&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YGwhmXJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYGwhmXJ.png&h=8e8bb265&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n(科普)作為一個工程佬等我話比你知黨鐵最煩既設備係咩！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1594466\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1594466</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n港鐵中環站早前停電疑電掣房滴水引致<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=183138&amp;refer=\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D183138%26refer%3D&d=%2FSZuxPcvMLfRWwfRMm0dxFm6lgSi2KDQroqMKj6vOm8%3D&h=9f2d93bc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D183138%26refer%3D&h=a1a4f75c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=183138&amp;refer=</a><br />\n<br />\n香港港鐵停電三綫延誤 乘客逼爆月台<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.singtaousa.com/日報/香港/219912-港鐵停電三綫延誤-乘客逼爆月台/\" data-sr-url=\"https://